SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION A, LINE 3
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: IN ACCORDANCE WITH SUNY GUIDELINES, COLLEGE AUXILIARY SERVICES OF THE STATE UNIVERSITY COLLEGE AT PLATTSBURGH, INC. IS THE ORGANIZATION'S FISCAL AGENT AND PERFORMS MANY OF THE ORGANIZATION'S ACCOUNTING AND CASH MANAGEMENT DUTIES.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION A, LINE 6
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: STUDENTS WHO PAY THE MANDATORY FEE ARE MEMBERS OF THE STUDENT ASSOCIATION.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION A, LINE 7A
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: MEMBERS OF THE STUDENT ASSOCIATION ELECT MEMBERS OF THE GOVERNING BODY.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 11B
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE FISCAL AGENT'S CONTROLLER REVIEWS THE FORM 990 FOR ACCURACY AND CONFORMITY WITH THE ORGANIZATION'S ACCOUNTING RECORDS BEFORE FILING.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 12C
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: ON AN ANNUAL BASIS, STUDENT ASSOCIATION OFFICERS AND SENATORS ARE REQUIRED TO COMPLETE UPDATED CONFLICT OF INTEREST FORMS AND DISCLOSE ANY CONFLICTS THAT EXIST.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION C, LINE 19
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: FINANCIAL STATEMENTS ARE FILED IN COLLEGE LIBRARY, AND OTHER DOCUMENTS ARE AVAILABLE UPON REQUEST.
